Absa Investors Worried by Ramos Joining Richemont Board, Business Day Says

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-05-09T05:32:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-09/absa-investors-worried-by-ramos-joining-richemont-board-business-day-says.html
Absa Group Ltd. (ASA)  investors are worried
the appointment of Chief Executive Officer  Maria Ramos  to the
board of Cie. Financiere Richemont SA will take as much as a
month out of her schedule, Johannesburg-based Business Day said,
citing unidentified shareholders.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  